title: The One Where Lala Does NYC, Boob Tape & Veganism
description:
Lala spent a wild week in New York City promoting the new paperback version of her book, “Give Them Lala,” which included stops at “Watch What Happens Live” (where lots did happen), and the Tamron Hall Show (featuring some emotional moments), and an upsetting walk through Central Park. Lala also details a recent encounter with an LA paparazzi photog, and answers a few voicemails. Plus, if you listen closely, you just might hear Ocean make her verbal podcast debut!
